# Karaf Agent

Using Apache Karaf to create Agents

--- name:content

To use [Apache Karaf](http://felix.apache.org/site/karaf-users-guide.html) as an Agent in the Test Cloud you will need to get a build or distro. 

Then you need to install the cloudmix agent feature.

    bin/karaf
    features:addUrl mvn:org.fusesource.cloudmix/features/1.3-SNAPSHOT/xml/features
    features:install cloudmix.agent 

